data.text:
Solomon Eldridge GOTHAM [Parents] 1 was born 2, 3 on 6 Jan 1840 in Jefferson Co., NY. Solomon married 4 Clara Kendall HOWE on 12 Dec 1860.

Thomas BLACK [Parents] 1, 2 was born 3, 4 on 9 Jul 1827 in Tartaraghan, Armagh, Ireland. He died 5 on 11 Apr 1901. He was buried 6 in Grindstone Island Upper Cemetery, Jefferson Co., NY. Thomas married 7 Caroline A. BENSON on 4 Mar 1854 in Kingston, Ontario, Canada.

Caroline A. BENSON [Parents] 1, 2, 3 was born 4, 5 about 1833 in Ireland. She died 6 in 1922. She was buried 7 in Grindstone Island Upper Cemetery, Jefferson Co., NY. Caroline married 8 Thomas BLACK on 4 Mar 1854 in Kingston, Ontario, Canada.

[Notes]

Thomas BLACK [Parents] 1 was born 2 in 1804 in Drumcree, Armagh, Northern Ireland. He died 3 on 16 Jun 1869 in Allora. He was buried on 17 Jun 1869 in Allora. Thomas married 4 Margaret KINGSBOROUGH on 20 Oct 1824 in Drumcree, Armagh, Northern Ireland.

Vernie HILL 1 was born 2 on 4 Dec 1868. She died 3, 4 on 13 May 1955 in Alexandria Bay, Jefferson Co., NY. Vernie married Clarence E. RICKETT.

Walter E. KITTLE Jr. [Parents] 1, 2 was born 3, 4 on 13 Dec 1926 in Clayton, Jefferson Co., NY. He died 5, 6 in Mar 1995 in Watertown, Jefferson Co., NY. He was buried 7 in St. Mary's Cemetery, Clayton, Jefferson Co., NY. Walter married 8, 9 Eleanor K. REFF on 2 Jun 1948 in Clayton, Jefferson Co., NY.
